com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.describehet

Class PdbDescribeHetNodeDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.NodeDialogPane
      • org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.DefaultNodeSettingsPane
        • com.vernalis.pdbconnector.nodes.describehet.PdbDescribeHetNodeDialog

  • public class PdbDescribeHetNodeDialog
extends org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.DefaultNodeSettingsPane
    NodeDialog for the "PdbDescribeHet" Node. Node to retrieve Heterogen details from the PDB "Describe Heterogen" webservice This node dialog derives from DefaultNodeSettingsPane which allows creation of a simple dialog with standard components. If you need a more complex dialog please derive directly from NodeDialogPane.
    Author:
    S.Roughley
